[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛本行集經卷第五十七",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隋天竺三藏闍那崛多譯",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "難陀因緣品下",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，佛告長老難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是如是。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人親近諸惡知識，共為朋友，交往止住，雖經少時共相隨順，後以惡業相染習故，令其惡聲名聞遠至。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊因斯事故，而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「猶如在於魚鋪上，　　以手執取一把茅，",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其人手即同魚臭，　　親近惡友亦如是。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊又共長老難陀，至於一賣香邸，見彼邸上有諸香裹，見已即告長老難陀作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「難陀！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝來取此邸上諸香裹物。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」難陀爾時即依佛教，於彼邸上取諸香裹。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝於漏刻一移之頃，捉持香裹然後放地。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c15_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老難陀聞佛如此語已，手持此香於一刻間，還放地上。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，佛告長老難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今當自嗅於手看。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c18_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，難陀聞佛語已，即嗅自手。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛語難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝嗅此手作何等氣？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」白言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其手香氣，微妙無量。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛告難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是如是。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人親近諸善知識，恒常共居，隨順染習，相親近故，必定當得廣大名聞。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊因此事故，而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有手執沈水香，　　及以藿香麝香等，",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須臾執持香自染，　　親附善友亦復然。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0914c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊出迦毘羅婆蘇都城，至本住處，以此因緣，聚集大眾諸比丘已，即告長老難陀言曰：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「難陀！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今莫親近彼六群比丘，莫共彼等以為親友。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a02_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若其有人親近如是惡知識者，雖復與彼共為朋友，或時與彼互相承事，隨順彼等一切事業，但為惡人，共相親近，即得世間惡名流布。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長老難陀！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝若欲覓親友知識，當近比丘舍利弗，比丘大目連，比丘大迦葉，比丘迦旃延，比丘優樓頻䗍迦葉，那提迦葉，伽耶迦葉，優波斯那，摩訶俱郗那，摩訶孫陀，離波多等，諸比丘輩。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勸汝親近隨順承事。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人親近善知識者，承事親善，雖未證得利益之事，交獲世間名聞流布。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊以此因緣而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若人親近惡知識，　　現世不得好名聞，",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "必以惡友相親近，　　當來亦墮阿鼻獄。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人親近善知識，　　隨順彼等所業行，",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖不現證世間利，　　未來當得盡苦因。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊雖以善言教示難陀，而彼難陀猶戀王位自在之樂，憶孫陀利五欲之事，於佛法中猶不欣樂，欲捨梵行，欲捨具戒，還從家事。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊知彼長老難陀心已，作如是念：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「然此難陀煩惱熾盛，豈能小教破彼煩惱，我於今者須作方便，喻如世間以火滅火、以毒治毒。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，執彼長老難陀之手，從尼俱陀樹林而出，以神通力隱沒其身，忽然在於香醉山上，出現而住。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，彼山以風吹故，兩樹相揩遂即出火，燒然彼山，出大煙炎。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915a29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼山內，多有獼猴，其數五百，被火燒毛，皆悉存地，摩滅身火。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊見有一箇雌瞎獼猴在彼群內，亦復以手撲滅身火。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，佛告長老難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今見此雌瞎獼猴在彼群內，亦復以手滅其身火如此已不？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，難陀白佛言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是如是，我今已見。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊尋復告彼長老難陀，作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝意云何？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝孫陀利，可憙端嚴，與此獼猴，是誰為勝？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，難陀遂向世尊，顰眉蹙面，默然不言。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊執持長老難陀手臂，從香醉山沒身往至三十三天，現於波利質多羅樹。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，彼樹下有一大石，名曰婆奴唫逆林反摩羅隋言黃褐，住於彼處。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，帝釋天王往入彼園，遊戲其園，名曰伊迦分陀利，將領五百宮人婇女，左右圍遶，作倡伎樂。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於時世尊見帝釋王，在彼伊迦分陀利園將領五百婇女，音聲歡娛受樂。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，佛即告長老難陀作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今見此五百婇女作倡伎樂遊戲已不？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」難陀白言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b20_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今已見。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊尋復告彼長老難陀作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝意云何？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為當釋女孫陀利好？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為當五百婇女端正？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」長老難陀白言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如以彼時雌瞎獼猴，與孫陀利共相比挍，百倍不如，乃至千倍，至百千倍，世間算數亦不可及。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今如是孫陀利女，欲令比此婇女五百，亦復不如百倍千倍，至百千倍世間算數所不能及。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915b29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今者云何可為比喻？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，佛告長老難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今意欲共此婇女相娛樂不？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，難陀歡喜踊躍，白言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如我意者，實欲與彼五百婇女共相娛樂。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，佛告長老難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今不可以此凡身共彼娛樂，若欲然者，必須以汝歡喜之心，於我法中行於梵行，我當報汝：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『今者若能隨順此法，行清淨行，命終捨身，於未來世，必得受報生於此處，共此五百諸婇女輩共相娛樂。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」爾時，難陀聞此事已，歡喜踊躍，遍滿其體，不能自勝，而白佛言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我從今日於佛法中，歡喜行於清淨梵行。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今者已許報我，我今實欲當未來世生於此處，共此五百諸婇女等，共相娛樂。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復執長老難陀臂已，從彼三十三天沒身，還其本處。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，難陀作如是念：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊於先已許報我於未來世，當得共彼五百婇女，以相娛樂。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是故難陀，以此因緣，盡其身心，正念行於清淨梵行，調伏諸根，節量飲食，初夜後夜，起誦經行，勇猛精進，不共他人言談戲笑；",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c21_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不躁急，心無狡猾，口不綺言，發精進行，念四威儀，樂於空寂，閉塞諸根，成就最勝微妙正念。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，難陀若欲意觀東方之時，安定身心，志意充滿，既正念已，然後方始觀於東方。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是觀時，無有愁惱，無有黑闇，於不善法，終無漏失，亦不迷惑。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是欲觀南西北方上方下方，亦定身心，志意充滿。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是觀時，亦無愁惱，無有黑闇，於不善法，更不漏失，亦不迷惑。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0915c29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，難陀或有同行諸比丘輩，而告之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長老難陀！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝於先時，不閉諸根，於諸飲食，不知厭足，恒求妙好床褥臥具安隱睡眠，本無厭勌，或時戲笑，心意不定，狡猾䛴語，不曾精勤，恒常懈怠，亦無正念，多諸忘失，威儀漏缺，無禪無定，不能攝心，諸根逸浪，不可具說。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何今者諸根調伏，飲食知足，初夜後夜不曾睡眠，無復狡戲，攝𣫍身心，又不䛴語，勇猛精進，正念正勤，已得禪定，心不漏逸，諸根不浪？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長老今日，何因得爾？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，難陀告彼同行諸比丘言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸長老輩！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知世尊於未來世，將欲報我五百婇女，歡娛受樂，是故我今於此法中，勤行梵行。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，難陀親友同行諸比丘等，於彼難陀欲有調笑嘲弄譏戲，各相謂言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長老難陀！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於世尊所，客作傭力，求將來報，故於法中勤行梵行。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長老難陀！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝於佛邊，行梵行者，正為諸天五百玉女行梵行耳？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老難陀親友諸比丘等，從爾已後，是故常喚為客作者。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊見此難陀為諸玉女行於梵行，遂便執臂，從彼尼拘陀林而出，沒身入於大地獄裏。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊於時見一銅釜下然猛火，其釜爀赤與火無異，出大光炎，熾然赩赩。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a24_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊見已，告彼難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝往問此諸獄卒等，此之銅釜欲為阿誰熾然湧沸？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃至如是長老難陀，聞佛是語白言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯如佛教。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即往詣彼諸獄卒邊而問之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此大銅釜，欲為何人如是湧沸乃至此也？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時獄卒，咸報難陀，作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916a29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛有姨母所生之弟，名曰難陀，為彼人故，燒然此釜。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」難陀復問：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝豈不聞？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來往日，許報其人，若為五百天樂婇女行於梵行，後得生於三十三天。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」諸獄卒言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是如是，我等已知。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但我等輩，復聞其人於彼三十三天之上墮落已後，來生此處。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，難陀聞此語已，心生恐怖，舉身毛竪，作如是念：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我若次第於此受苦，我今亦欲不用如此婇女果報。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊即執長老難陀臂已，從地獄內，隱沒其身，還至尼俱陀林而出。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，難陀為己同行諸親友等，恒常喚作佛客作人，被笑被呵，嘲調戲弄。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復見地獄，慚愧恐怖，即生厭離，自悼自悔，求空閑處，獨行獨坐，更不放逸，精進勇猛。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "凡善男子，其有正信捨家出家，求於無上清淨梵行，行已現得自證神通，得諸漏盡，口自唱言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「生死已盡，梵行已立，所作已辦，不受後有。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」證羅漢果，心得解脫。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b19_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "長老難陀亦復如是，證羅漢果，然後始往至於佛所，頂禮佛足，却坐一面。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，長老難陀白佛作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今捨世尊往日恩許，我昔欲取如來報者，正為五百諸天婇女，是故如此；",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而今，世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得解脫也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，佛告長老難陀：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「非但今日我於汝邊始得脫也，汝初唱言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『梵行已立，所作已辦，不受後有。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』我於彼時，已得脫也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916b27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老難陀同行諸比丘等，未知難陀得漏盡者，猶如先日未漏盡時，戲弄謿調，唱如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「長老難陀於世尊所，客作求報，為彼五百諸天婇女，行於梵行。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊作如是念：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等比丘未知難陀諸漏已盡，還依昔日未漏盡時，猶故唱言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『長老難陀為彼諸天五百婇女，行於梵行。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』我恐彼等多獲罪過。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然我今者，可於眾中宣揚顯說長老難陀漏盡事也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊以如此等因緣事故，集聚一切諸比丘僧，既聚集已，而告之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝諸比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有人言好男子者，難陀比丘即其人也；",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若言端正，亦即難陀比丘是也；",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大壯人者，難陀比丘亦其人也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若言身體細軟弱者，亦復難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若言有人諸根寂靜不散亂者，亦復難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有人言於諸飲食知節量者，亦復難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若有人言初夜後夜不睡眠者，今亦難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若言三族清淨生者，亦即難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有人言得六通者，此亦難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若言得八解脫定者，亦復難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊告比丘僧作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝諸比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於我聲聞弟子之內，調伏諸根，難陀比丘最為第一。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，諸比丘而問佛言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其彼長老難陀比丘，往昔之時，有何善根？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "因彼善根，生於釋種甚大富貴，豐足資財，其人身體端正可憙。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊今日復記云：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0916c29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我聲聞弟子，調伏諸根，最第一者，難陀比丘即其人也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」作是語已，佛告彼等諸比丘言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝諸比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我念往昔九十一劫，時有一佛出現於世，名毘婆尸多他竭多、阿羅呵、三藐三佛陀，如來、應供、正遍知、明行足、善逝、世間解、無上士、調御丈夫、天人師、佛、世尊，於彼世界王所居住。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼有一城，名槃徒摩低，於時彼佛依彼城住，有諸比丘六千人，俱皆阿羅漢。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有一王名曰槃頭，供養彼佛及比丘僧，尊重恭敬，所謂衣服臥具飲食，及諸湯藥房舍之具，無所乏少。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時，槃頭摩低城內有一種姓婆羅門子，而彼童子營造溫室，請佛及僧洗浴供養。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其婆羅門種姓童子，見諸比丘從溫室出，身體清淨，甚大香潔無有臭氣，見已心生歡喜，踊躍遍滿其體，不能自勝，心發是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世，常得如是清淨無垢不腥臭身，當似如是比丘僧等清淨香潔無臭之身。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』又於後時，毘婆尸佛、多他伽多、阿羅呵、三藐三佛陀，入般涅槃，其王槃頭，為彼世尊所有舍利，取四種寶，為造塔廟，所謂金銀琉璃頗梨。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時彼種姓婆羅門子，撿挍經營，當造彼塔。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既造塔已，心作是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世恒常值遇如是世尊，彼所說法，願我領解悉得證知，莫背彼法，生生世世不入惡道。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』而彼童子命終之後，恒生天上，或生人間，於後一生，生一大富長者之家，父母養育，隨時長大，意智漸漸，皆得成就。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時，童子其家恒有一辟支佛，為作門師，數數至家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917a28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼辟支佛，可憙端正，具足三十大丈夫相，而彼童子恒以四事供養供給彼辟支佛，盡其一形，無所乏少。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其辟支佛盡其住世，然後涅槃。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時，長者見辟支佛命終涅槃，即取彼身，如法闍毘，收取舍利，起塔供養，以泥塗飾復以石灰，重塗其上。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以莊嚴故，懸諸種種寶珠瓔珞，發是願言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我未來恒值如是辟支世尊，而彼世尊所說之法，聞已領解，永不忘失，生生世世不墮惡道。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦願我身，端正可憙，見者歡喜，身有三十大丈夫相，具足無減，如此大仙等無有異。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』而彼長者捨身命終，後更不曾生於惡道，恒生人天，久久流轉，於後復生波羅㮈國。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼時有王名吉利尸隋言瘦細，以為彼子。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於爾之時乃有一佛，出現於世，名曰迦葉多他伽多、阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然彼世尊隨其住世，滅度已後，吉利尸王純以七寶，為造塔廟，所謂金銀頗梨琉璃，及赤真珠珊瑚馬瑙。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其寶塔外，更以麤塼重覆其上，其塔高峻至一由旬，東西縱廣各半由旬，為作銘記，名曰達舍婆陵迦隋云十相。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「爾時，吉利尸王所生七子僉白王言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善哉大王！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知我等欲於迦葉多他伽多、阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀舍利塔上，各各奉施一大傘蓋以覆其塔。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉大王！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願垂聽許。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』王告之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『任隨汝等！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今聽造。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「爾時，彼等諸七王子各以一寶，造其一蓋，覆其塔上，或造金蓋，或造銀蓋，乃至或造碼瑙等蓋。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其七子內，第二王子，造其金蓋，以覆塔上，心發是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世恒值如是辟支佛尊，彼所說法，願我領證，永不忘失，生生世世，不墮惡道，所生之處，願得猶如金色之身。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」爾時，佛告諸比丘等：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝諸比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有心疑，於彼槃頭摩城之內，婆羅門子，供養彼佛及比丘僧，溫室洗浴，心發是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世，當得似此比丘僧眾清淨無垢香潔之身。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』於毘婆尸多他伽多、阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀滅度之後，造塔供養之童子者？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "莫作異見，此即難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝諸比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等若有疑彼長者，一形供養彼辟支佛，滅後復以舍利起塔，供養塗治，及以石灰種種莊飾，及諸瓔珞供養彼塔，心作是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世如此辟支端正可憙，觀者無厭，身有三十大丈夫相，具足無減，如此仙人。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』蓋是誰也？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝諸比丘莫作異見，此亦難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝諸比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等若有心疑，於彼波羅㮈城吉利尸王第二之子，為彼迦葉多他伽多阿羅訶三藐三佛陀，造作金蓋以覆塔者，莫作異見，此亦難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「然此難陀以於往昔毘婆尸佛及比丘僧，為作溫室，如法洗浴，因發是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世，當得如是清淨香潔無垢之身，如此比丘清淨無垢。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』又復供養辟支佛尊，尊滅度後起舍利塔，以泥塗治石灰嚴飾，并以瓔珞而莊挍之，心作是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世，如是端正，如是可憙，身有三十大丈夫相，具足無減，如此仙人。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』復於迦葉多他伽多、阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀滅度之後，造舍利塔，純金造蓋以覆其上，心發是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世所生之處，身恒金色。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0917c29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』藉彼業緣，今成如此可憙端正觀者無厭金色之身，復有三十大丈夫相，皆悉具足，無有缺減。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於彼之時，復起心願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世，勿生惡道。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a03_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』藉彼業報，不曾生於惡道之內，恒得生於人天道中。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復於彼時，毘婆尸佛、多他伽多、阿羅訶、三藐三佛陀造塔之時，撿挍經紀，於辟支佛復以四事，盡形供養。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "藉彼業報因緣力故，今得生於釋種之家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於爾時，心發是願：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『願我來世，常得值遇如是世尊，或勝此者，然彼世尊所有法教，願我聞已，速得證解。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』藉彼業報因緣力故，今得值我，即於我邊，而得出家及具足戒，我復授記，告諸比丘：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『若知於我聲聞弟子調伏諸根最第一者，難陀比丘即其人也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「汝諸比丘！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等須知，難陀比丘昔日造作如是善根，藉彼善根，今得生於釋種之家，身有金色，具足三十大丈夫相，現得出家，受具足戒，得羅漢果，復得授記作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a18_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『若欲知我聲聞弟子調伏諸根最第一者，所謂難陀比丘是也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」58 婆提唎迦等因緣品1佛本行集經婆提唎迦等因緣品第五十八上爾時，提婆達多釋種童子，見諸五百釋童子等捨家出家，心發是念：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今亦可於世尊所捨家出家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，至父母邊，白如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a25_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉父母！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今發心將欲佛邊捨家出家，願垂許我。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是語已，父母即告提婆達多釋童子言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等今者作是思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我等須依提婆達多，提婆達多復須依我。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918a29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』既如此者，隨汝意樂，當作是事。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，提婆達多童子身著上妙無價衣服，乘最勝象，從迦毘羅婆蘇都城欲出城外，於城門頰，為鉤所掛，衣裳破裂。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於彼之時，有一解相大婆羅門，在邊而見，其彼見已，記此童子，所規之事必當不成。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，童子提婆達多即出城已，詣向佛所，頂禮佛足，却住一面，而白佛言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯願世尊！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "放我出家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊正念觀彼提婆達多前後事業，知其心行，觀已即告提婆達多作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「提婆達多！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今慎莫捨家出家，但當還家在家修道，持諸財錢，以用布施，作諸功德，於我法中，不須出家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，童子提婆達多被佛訶已，復至長老舍利弗邊，而白之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「聖者舍利弗！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "與我出家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b16_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老舍利弗問提婆達多作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「提婆達多！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝曾先至佛邊已不？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」提婆達多報言聖者：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我先已曾至佛邊也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老舍利弗言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「提婆達多！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊向汝，作何言說？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」提婆達多語舍利弗：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是聖者！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊語我：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝莫捨家而出家也，但當在家行其布施作諸功德；",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若其在我法中出家，汝無利益。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」爾時，長老舍利弗作如是念：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊今者既不聽彼於法出家，我今若放彼出家者，是我不善。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是念已，遂即告彼提婆達多作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b26_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「提婆達多！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如世尊教，汝必應當作如是事。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918b27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，童子提婆達多被舍利弗之所發遣，復詣長老目揵連邊，到已頂禮，却住一面，而白之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大目揵連！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯願聖者！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "與我出家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老大目揵連，遂復告彼提婆達多作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「提婆達多！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝曾於先至佛邊不？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」提婆達多報言聖者：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我已於先至佛邊也。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c04_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於時長老大目揵連尋復告彼提婆達多，作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊語汝，有何事意？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」提婆達多復報之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊語我：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝莫於此捨家出家，但當如法在家修道，以財布施作諸功德，不須於我法中出家，若出家者於汝無益。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」爾時，長老大目揵連亦復報彼提婆達多，作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如世尊教！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c11_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝必應當作如是事。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，提婆達多既被目連不許出家，復詣長老大迦葉所，乃至略說，悉如前事，次復詣於迦旃延邊。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次復至於優樓頻螺迦葉之邊，次復至於長老那提迦葉之邊。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次復至於長老優波斯那之邊，及至摩訶俱郗羅邊，摩訶孫陀離波多邊，悉皆不許。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既不許已，方乃詣向長老優波離波多邊，頂禮優波離波多足，却住一面。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，提婆達多釋種童子，復從優波離波多邊，請乞出家。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然其長老優波離波多，復問之言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「提婆達多！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝應於先往到佛所。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」提婆達多報言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「聖者！",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於先日，已至佛邊。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，長老優波離波多作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝至佛邊，語汝何事？",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」提婆達多作如是言：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊語我：",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c26_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝莫於此捨家出家，但當在家如法修道，以財布施，作諸功德，不須於我法中出家，若出家者於汝無益。",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0918c29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」佛本行集經卷第五十七",
        "from": "T03n0190_057:0919a01_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]